===自發性勃起===
自發性勃起主要發生在無意識的情況下，其通常在睡眠期間發生{{sfn|Ульянова|2009|page=27}}。自發性勃起是一種正常現象，可出現在不同年齡的人身上，甚至在子宮內成長期間就可以出現<ref>{{cite web
 |url         = http://www.livestrong.com/article/267344-erections-in-babies/
 |title       = Erections in Babies
 |author      = Holly L. Roberts
 |date        = 2011-06-14
 |work        = 
 |publisher   = 
 |accessdate  = 2012-09-17
 |archiveurl  = https://www.webcitation.org/6BS446EpS?url=http://www.livestrong.com/article/267344-erections-in-babies/
 |archivedate = 2012-10-16
 |dead-url    = no
}}</ref>。但若它在公眾場所等當事人不希望發生的場合下發生，其便可能會感到[[尷尬|尷尬]]<ref name="Madaras2007"/>。自發性勃起可在一天內任何時間發生，並可能會使褲襠出現凸起。這種情況可透過穿著貼身的內褲或寬鬆的衣服來掩饰<ref name="Attwood2008">{{cite book|author=Sarah Attwood|title=Making Sense of Sex: A Forthright Guide to Puberty, Sex and Relationships for People with Asperger's Syndrome|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=xLqwYAzogiwC&pg=PA62|accessdate=22 July 2013|date=15 May 2008|publisher=Jessica Kingsley Publishers|isbn=978-1-84642-797-8|page=62}}</ref>。
====夜間陰莖勃起====
{{main|夜間陰莖勃起}}
陰莖可在睡眠中或剛睡醒時勃起。這一現像在醫學上稱為[[夜間陰莖勃起|夜間陰莖勃起]]（俗稱晨勃）<ref>[http://www.sizemed.com/morning-erections/ Morning Erections: Sizemed] {{Wayback|url=http://www.sizemed.com/morning-erections/ |date=20170521081021 }} retrieved 28 February 2012</ref><ref>After Prostate Cancer: A What-Comes-Next Guide to a Safe and Informed recovery: p.48</ref><ref>Listen To Your Hormones, Abraham Harvey Kryger - 2004. p.32</ref><ref>{{cite book|author=Janell L. Carroll|title=Sexuality Now: Embracing Diversity: Embracing Diversity|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=5f8mQx7ULs4C&pg=PA149|date=29 January 2009|publisher=Cengage Learning|isbn=978-0-495-60274-3|page=149}}</ref>。所有沒有[[勃起障礙|勃起障礙]]的男性都有經歷過晨間勃起，一般來說一晚會經過三到五次，特別是[[快速動眼期|快速動眼睡眠]]（{{lang|en|REM sleep}}）期間<ref name="WebMD">{{cite web
